msgstr "lloji jo"

#: lib/Domain/Service/DnsValidation/IPSECKEYRecordValidator.php:187
msgid ""
"IPSECKEY algorithm must be 0 (No key), 1 (RSA), 2 (DSA), 3 (ECDSA), or 4 "
