#: templates/modern/list_networks.html:15
msgid ""
"Each network (CIDR block) maps to exactly one view. Resolvers in that "
"network receive only the zone variants assigned to the mapped view. PowerDNS"
" evaluates networks longest-prefix first, so a more specific subnet (for "
